high_descs: Pick up the plunger from the ground.
Bring the plunger to the sink.
Put the plunger in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the plunger in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to go to the toilet.
Pick up the plunger that is on the left side of the toilet.
Turn and go to the sink with the plunger.
Open the cabinet door under the left side under the sink.  Place the plunger in the front middle of the cabinet.  Shut the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Move the plunger to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the door, turn right, walk to the toilet
Take the toilet plunger on the floor
Turn right and walk to the cabinet by the toilet
Open the cabinet, put the plunger in, close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Move the plunger from the floor to the cabinet by the toilet
